Subject: [PATCH 02/13] fix(copilot): reset _inherited_permissions contextvar
 after each execution

Mirrors the _check_recursion/_reset_recursion pattern: _merge_inherited_permissions
now returns a reset token, and execute_copilot resets it in its finally block.
Also removes empty TYPE_CHECKING block in permissions.py and moves
get_current_permissions import to module level in run_block.py.
